&lt;p&gt;Located within the Palermo Hollywood sub-neighborhood of Palermo best known for it&amp;#8217;s lively culinary + nightlife scene, Osaka is one of the most exciting restaurants in Buenos Aires. Featuring the renowned Nikkei- style cuisine of Chef Ciro Watanabe, Osaka Palermo is chic and hip. Dress to impress.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please &lt;a title=&quot;Osaka - Palermo&quot; href=&quot;http://osaka.com.pe/osaka-buenos-aires-palermo/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;book online&lt;/a&gt; or contact Osaka Palermo by phone at +54 11 4775 6964&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: As a courtesy Osaka asks for 24 hour cancelation notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advance booking recommendation: Osaka recommends booking with 48 hours advance notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must use your Diners Club Card for payment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preferred bookings based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

